high_descs: Turn around and go straight back to the sink on the right.
Pick up the tomato from the left side of the sink.
Carry the tomato and turn right to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the tomato inside. Shut the door then open it and take out the tomato.
Carry the tomato and turn to the left, then left at the counter.
Place the tomato on the counter, to the right of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Chill a tomato and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn left in front of the counter
Pick up the tomato on the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn left in front of the fridge
Put the tomato in the fridge, wait, pick up the tomato from the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward to the counter
Put the tomato on the counter
anns.task_desc: Cool a tomato and put it on the counter

high_descs: Walk to the counter by the sink
Grab the tomato that is on the  sink dry  board
carry the tomato to the fridge
put the tomato in the fridge. then take it out
carry the tomato to the counter that has the toaster
Set the tomato down on the counter
anns.task_desc: place a chilled tomato on the counter
